** Heading +Sym
** CalculiX static analysis template — cantilever beam
** Rendered by AI-FEA Solver Agent from SimPlan parameters.
**
** Variables (Jinja2):
**   mesh_include   — path to .inp mesh file (Abaqus format from Gmsh)
**   material_name  — e.g. "Steel"
**   youngs_modulus  — Pa
**   poissons_ratio
**   load_magnitude  — N
**   load_node_set   — name of the node set receiving the load
**   fixed_node_set  — name of the fixed-BC node set
**
** This template is a minimal stub (AI-FEA-P0-01).
** It will be expanded with multi-step, thermal, and modal blocks in P0-07.
